This repo contains a MapReduce implementation of Vector Space Model of Information Retrieval. 

Scripts : 
1. MapReduce.py - implements mapreduce in python
2. inverted_index - computes inverted index of tf-idf vectors
3. length.py - computes lengths of tf-idf vectors
4. cosine.py - computes cosine similarity with a specific query and returns documents ordered to their relevance. 

Procedure : 
Offline - 
1. python inverted_index "input_corpus_of_documents" > index.txt
2. python length.py index.txt > vector_lengths.txt

Online - 
1. Enter the query in cosine.py
2. python cosine.py vector_length.txt index.txt > output.txt
